== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2008年6月，華納兄弟公司聯繫了漫畫作家、編劇和導演一起研究應該如何成功地重啟超人系列電影<ref>{{cite news | author = Josh Wigler | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/03/26/mark-millar-on-his-superman-movie-trilogy-nothing-is-happening | title = Mark Millar On His 'Superman' Movie Trilogy: 'Nothing Is Happening' | work = MTV News | date = 2009-03-26 | accessdate = 2010-12-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100428081412/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/03/26/mark-millar-on-his-superman-movie-trilogy-nothing-is-happening/ | archivedate = 2010-04-28 }}</ref>，“我告訴他們這是個不錯的點子，只管像看待[[李安|李安]]的《[[綠巨人浩克_(電影)|綠巨人]]》一樣來看待《超人歸來》。”漫畫小說作家馬克·韋德（Mark Waid）解釋道，“《[[無敵浩克|無敵浩克]]》已經證明，觀眾會原諒你，他們也願意接受新的版本”<ref name=Jen>{{cite news | author = Jennifer Vineyard | title = How To Reboot The Superman Movie Franchise-Comic Writers Chime In | publisher = MTV | date = 2008-08-11 | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/08/11/how-to-reboot-the-superman-movie-franchise-comic-writers-chime-in/ | accessdate = 2008-08-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131013052908/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/08/11/how-to-reboot-the-superman-movie-franchise-comic-writers-chime-in/ | archivedate = 2013-10-13 }}</ref>。漫畫小說作家格蘭特·莫里森、高夫·強斯和布拉德·梅特澤都對電影的重啟給出了自己的想法。莫里森的構思與他創作的《全明星超人》類似，而韋德的方案則與《超人：與生俱來的權利》相仿<ref name=Jen/>。馬克·米勒和導演[[馬修·沃恩|馬修·沃恩]]則計劃了一套長達8個小時的三部曲，每一年發行一部，與《魔戒》三部曲相似<ref>{{cite news | author = Martin Anderson | title = The Den Of Geek interview: Mark Millar | publisher = DenofGeek.com | date = 2008-07-20 | url = http://www.denofgeek.com/comics/88459/the_den_of_geek_interview_mark_millar.html | accessdate = 2008-08-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080827185000/http://www.denofgeek.com/comics/88459/the_den_of_geek_interview_mark_millar.html | archivedate = 2008-08-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Josh Wigler | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/26/matthew-vaughn-superman | title = Matthew Vaughn Says 'Superman' Movie Discussions Were 'Very Brief' | work = MTV News | date = 2010-03-26 | accessdate = 2010-12-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100915005822/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/26/matthew-vaughn-superman/ | archivedate = 2010-09-15 }}</ref>。米勒則建議以《教父》三部曲的模式來設計劇情，即包含有超人早期在氪星出生和成長，到最終失去超強力的一生寫照<ref>{{cite news | author =  | title = Exclusive: Mark Millar Talks Superman | publisher = EmpireOnline | date = 2008-10-29 | url = http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=23521 | accessdate = 2008-10-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131102103809/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=23521 | archivedate = 2013-11-02 }}</ref>。 2009年8月，法院裁決傑里·西格爾一家人重新獲得超人的電影版權<ref>{{cite news|author=Marc Graser|title=Superman co-creator's family given rights|publisher=Variety|date= 2009-08-13|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118007269.html|accessdate=2009-08-29}}</ref>。法院也裁決華納兄弟公司沒有因拍攝之前的《超人》系列電影而欠下西格爾一家任何專利費用，但是如果新版的超人電影一直到2011年還沒有開拍，那麼西格爾就可以再以未拍攝電影的利潤損失為由起訴華納兄弟公司要求賠償<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118005806.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 |title=Warner Bros. wins ' Superman' case |author=McNary, Dave |date=2009-07-08 |work=Variety |accessdate=2010-07-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100630170321/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118005806.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 |archivedate=2010-06-30 }}</ref>。

2010年對《[[黑暗騎士：黎明昇起|黑暗騎士：黎明昇起]]》的故事進行探討時，[[大衛·S·高耶|大衛·S·高耶]]得知華納兄弟公司正在策劃重啟超人電影系列，於是告知了[[克里斯托弗·諾蘭|克里斯托弗·諾蘭]]自己所構思的現代背景超人故事。諾蘭對此留下了深刻的印象，並於2010年2月聯繫華納兄弟公司提出了這一設想<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | url = http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/102090-christopher-nolan-on-batman-and-superman | title = Christopher Nolan on Batman and Superman | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2010-06-04 | accessdate = 2010-12-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110105182212/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/102090-christopher-nolan-on-batman-and-superman | archivedate = 2011-01-05 }} </ref>。考慮到《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》商業和評論上的成功<ref name="wall">{{Cite news|first = Lauren AE|last = Schuker|title = Warner Bets on Fewer, Bigger Movies|work = The Wall Street Journal|date = 2008-08-22|url = http://online.wsj.com/article/SB121936107614461929.html|accessdate = 2008-10-22|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5xLzZSe7O?url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB121936107614461929.html|archivedate = 2011-03-21}}. .</ref>，華納兄弟公司於是請諾蘭來出任這部新電影的製片人，並由高耶編劇<ref>{{cite news|title=It's A Bird! It's A Plane! It's Chris Nolan! He'll Mentor Superman 3.0 And Prep 3rd Batman|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2010-02-09|url=http://deadline.com/2010/02/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-chris-nolan-hell-mentor-superman-3-0-while-preparing-3rd-batman-24783/|accessdate=2010-12-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827103911/http://deadline.com/2010/02/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-chris-nolan-hell-mentor-superman-3-0-while-preparing-3rd-batman-24783/|archivedate=2014-08-27}}</ref>。諾蘭也曾像1978年理查德·唐納執導《超人》那樣來為《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》選擇演員，所以他也很讚賞辛格執導《[[超人归来|超人歸來]]》與老版電影聯繫起來的做法。“他們讓白蘭度、格倫·福特和尼德·巴蒂這些偉大的演員來扮演小角色，”諾蘭表示，“這在當時的超級英雄電影中可是個不同尋常的做法”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/03/christopher-nolan-takes-flight-with-superman-we-have-a-fantastic-story-1.html |title=Christopher Nolan takes flight with Superman: 'We have a fantastic story' [UPDATED] |last=Boucher |first=Geoff |date=2010-03-10 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher= |accessdate=2010-06-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704194608/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/03/christopher-nolan-takes-flight-with-superman-we-have-a-fantastic-story-1.html |archivedate=2010-07-04 }}</ref>。唐納的電影也給諾蘭的童年時代留下了深刻的印象，成為用來判斷電影質量好壞的參照標準<ref>{{cite news|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/06/28/christopher-nolan-superman-actor/|title=Does Christopher Nolan Want An Unknown Actor For Next 'Superman' Movie?|work=MTV News|date=2010-06-28|accessdate=2010-12-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100629225655/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/06/28/christopher-nolan-superman-actor/|archivedate=2010-06-29}}</ref>。[[吉爾莫·德爾·托羅|吉爾莫·德爾·托羅]]決定接拍小說《瘋狂山脈》改編的同名電影，因此拒絕了執導本片的邀請<ref>{{cite news |author = Michael Fleming |url = http://www.deadline.com/2010/09/toronto-qa-julias-eyes-and-biutiful-producer-guillermo-del-toro/ |title = Toronto Q&A: Guillermo Del Toro About Producing 'Julia's Eyes' And 'Biutiful' |work = Deadline.com |date = 2010-09-13 |accessdate = 2010-12-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120929235212/http://www.deadline.com/2010/09/toronto-qa-julias-eyes-and-biutiful-producer-guillermo-del-toro/ |archivedate = 2012-09-29 }}</ref>，之後公司聯繫了[[羅伯特·澤米基斯|羅伯特·澤米基斯]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Kevin Panasiewicz | url = http://collider.com/superman-reboot-robert-zemeckis-zack-snyder/ | title = Robert Zemeckis Passed On SUPERMAN Reboot “Faster than a Speeding Bullet” | work = collider | date = 2010-11-01 | accessdate = 2010-12-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180308103639/http://collider.com/superman-reboot-robert-zemeckis-zack-snyder/ | archivedate = 2018-03-08 }}</ref>。有傳言稱[[本·阿弗萊克|本·阿弗萊克]]曾考慮執導一部超人電影，他對此沒有否認，不過也表示自己主要是基於故事情節來選擇項目：“我所學到的一點是不要根據預算數額，或是花了多少錢在特技效果上以及在什麼地方取景拍攝來看待一部電影。故事才是最重要的”<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://www.deadline.com/2010/11/oscar-ben-affleck-qa-on-the-town/ | title = Oscar: Ben Affleck Q&A On 'The Town' | work = Deadline.com | date = 2010-11-26 | accessdate = 2010-12-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101130050517/http://www.deadline.com/2010/11/oscar-ben-affleck-qa-on-the-town/ | archivedate = 2010-11-30 }}</ref>。此外，華納兄弟公司還曾考慮由[[托尼·斯科特|托尼·斯科特]]、[[達倫·阿倫諾夫斯基|達倫·阿倫諾夫斯基]]、[[鄧肯·瓊斯|鄧肯·瓊斯]]、[[喬納森·里貝斯曼|喬納森·里貝斯曼]]和馬特·里夫斯來執導本片<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://www.deadline.com/2010/09/chris-nolan-looking-for-superman-director/ | title = Chris Nolan Looking for 'Superman' Directors | work = Deadline.com | date = 2010-09-23 | accessdate = 2010-12-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101124055929/http://www.deadline.com/2010/09/chris-nolan-looking-for-superman-director/ | archivedate = 2010-11-24 }}</ref>，但最終選中的是[[扎克·施奈德|扎克·施奈德]]，他於2010年10月加入<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/10/zack-snyder-directing-superman/ |title=SCOOP: Zack Snyder Directing 'Superman' |work=Deadline.com |author=Michael Fleming |date=2010-10-04 |accessdate=2010-10-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101005212534/http://www.deadline.com/2010/10/zack-snyder-directing-superman/ |archivedate=2010-10-05 }}</ref>，演員的敲定則在11月開始<ref>{{cite news | author = Mike Snider | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2010/11/qa-screenwriter-david-goyer-on-call-of-duty-black-ops/1 | title = Q&A: Screenwriter David Goyer on 'Call of Duty: Black Ops' | work = USA Today | date = 2010-11-26 | accessdate = 2010-12-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140612163121/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2010/11/qa-screenwriter-david-goyer-on-call-of-duty-black-ops/1 | archivedate = 2014-06-12 }}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
電影的拍攝工作於2011年8月1日在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]以西杜佩奇機場附近的一個工業園展開，工作代碼為“秋霜”（Autumn Frost）<ref name="ChicagoBusiness2">{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagobusiness.com/article/20110728/NEWS07/110729855/superman-flying-into-chicago-in-august-for-filming |first=Paul |last=Merrion |title=Superman flying into Chicago in August for filming |work=Crain's Chicago Business |date=2011-07-28 |accessdate=2011-07-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110818024029/http://www.chicagobusiness.com/article/20110728/NEWS07/110729855/superman-flying-into-chicago-in-august-for-filming |archivedate=2011-08-18 }}</ref>。扎克·施奈德表示考慮其格式上的局限性，自己不大情願將本片拍成[[三維電影|三維電影]]<ref name="3d">{{cite web |url=http://www.latinoreview.com/news/-superman-man-of-steel-3d-still-up-in-the-air-1309 |title='Superman: Man of Steel' 3D Still Up In The Air |work=Latino Review |date=2011-04-01 |accessdate=2011-11-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111326/http://www.latinoreview.com/news/-superman-man-of-steel-3d-still-up-in-the-air-1309 |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>，而是選擇先用傳統的2D方式拍攝，再在後期製作中將其轉換為3D<ref name="Snyder 3D">{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/superman-man-of-steel-post-converted-3d/ |title='Man of Steel' Being Post-Converted to 3D |work=Screen Rant |date=2012-11 |accessdate=2013-04-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130620110112/http://screenrant.com/superman-man-of-steel-post-converted-3d/ |archivedate=2013-06-20 }}</ref>。他還選擇了使用膠片攝影機而非數碼攝影機​​進行拍攝，因為他認為這樣可以讓電影有“大片體驗”<ref name="film">{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/04/17/cinemacon-warner-bros-gatsby-superman/2089599/ |title='Gatsby,' Superman make their introduction at CinemaCon |work=USA Today |date=2013-04-13 |accessdate=2013-04-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130422115714/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/04/17/cinemacon-warner-bros-gatsby-superman/2089599/ |archivedate=2013-04-22 }}</ref>。計劃拍攝時間約為兩到三個月<ref name="ChicagoBusiness">{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagobusiness.com/article/20110326/ISSUE01/303269971/latest-superman-movie-arrives-in-the-nick-of-time |first=Paul |last=Merrion |title=Latest Superman movie arrives in the nick of time |work=Crain's Chicago Business |date=2011-03-28 |accessdate=2011-07-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110803151916/http://www.chicagobusiness.com/article/20110326/ISSUE01/303269971/latest-superman-movie-arrives-in-the-nick-of-time |archivedate=2011-08-03 }}</ref>。 8月22至29日，製作在[[肯德爾縣_(伊利諾伊州)|肯德爾縣]]的一個名叫{{link-en|普拉諾 (伊利諾伊州)|Plano, Illinois|普拉諾}}的小城進行<ref name="ChicagoBusiness2"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/03/28/superman-man-of-steel-chicago_n_841436.html |title=''Superman: Man Of Steel'' Filming In Chicago, According To Industry Sources |last=Guzzardi |first=Will |accessdate=2011-03-29 |date=2011-03-28 |work=Huffington Post |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110409080143/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/03/28/superman-man-of-steel-chicago_n_841436.html |archivedate=2011-04-09 }}</ref>。據麥可·珊農在接受一次採訪時表示，電影的拍攝工作將持續至2012年2月<ref>{{cite web |first=Mark |last=Julian |url=http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/GraphicCity/news/?a=49156 |title=More From Michael Shannon On Zack Snyder's Man Of Steel And His General Zod Role |publisher=ComicBookMovie.com |date=2011-10-31 |accessdate=2012-05-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111102060032/http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/GraphicCity/news/?a=49156 |archivedate=2011-11-02 }}</ref>，片中的美軍也是請真的美軍來幫忙拍攝。

